Package com.ibm.itim.policy.sod

Interface Summary
IHierarchyConflicts Provides role conflict information for potential roles added to a separation of duty policy exclusion list.
IPolicyResult A IPolicyResult stores the Separation of Duty evaluation results for a given Person who was analyzed.
IPolicyRuleStatistics Provides violation and exemption counts for a given separation of duty policy rule.
IPolicyStatistics Provides violation and exemption counts for a given separation of duty policy.
IRuleExemption Interface for accessing Separation of Duty rule exemption information which was written to the database during a Separation of Duty approval activity.
IRuleResult IRuleResult stores the Separation of Duty rule evaluation results for a given Person who was analyzed.
IRuleViolation Interface for accessing Separation of Duty rule violation information which was evaluated and written to the database during a data synchronization.
